A FREE trade pact between Czechoslovakia and the European Free Trade
Association (Efta) comes into effect as planned today,despite uncertainty
over the future of the Czech and Slovak republics.
Mr Hans-Jorg Renk, Efta spokesman, said both sides would pursue 'business as
